anglais des sciences n’est pas exactement la langue de Shakespeare dans sa forme et ses fonctions; je préfère l’appeler la langue de Darwin. C’est pour en apprendre le style et les codes que je vous propose ce guide de rédaction.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aEnglish languagexGrammarvTextbooks for foreign speakersxFrench. 0aEnglish languagexTechnical English. 0aEnglish languagexWritten English. 0aTechnical writing. 7aLITERARY COLLECTIONS / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2016z978311127380808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2016z978311127630440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978276372839140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763728391423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763728391/original  a978-3-11-127380-8  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2016b2016  a978-3-11-127630-4  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2016b2016  aGBV-deGruyter-alles